snippet.title: Nitronic Rush: Release Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
WE'RE CREATING A SPIRITUAL SUCCESSOR TO NITRONIC RUSH CALLED DISTANCE! Back it on PayPal to get eventual access to the Beta! http://bit.ly/DistancePayPal

Nitronic Rush is an experimental survival driving game developed by students at DigiPen Institute of Technology. Using the car's many abilities (including boost, wings, and jump), avoid obstacles that the city throws at you. In many ways the game is a tribute to racing games of the 1990s, but with fresh graphics, audio, and gameplay.

Download now! http://nitronic-rush.com

The game was released on the PC platform (with support for Xbox 360 controllers) on November 11th, 2011. Visit our website below to download the game for free!

The song used in the trailer is called "End to a Violent Heart" and it's from the Nitronic Rush original soundtrack. Download the entire soundtrack here: http://bit.ly/NitronicRushOST

RT! http://bit.ly/NRTrailer | FB! http://on.fb.me/N5pVzS

Music and trailer by: TORCHT (http://twitter.com/torcht)
